full_readme:
EnsembleData's Tiktok API is a powerful scraper that allows users to effortlessly extract data from the Tiktok platform. With this tool, you can scrape various types of data such as:

📊 post info & stats
🙋 author metadata
📹 video metadata
🎧 audio metadata
📝 post comments
What are the costs?

We are currently offer this actor for free! There will be some minimal platform costs, but we aim to be as efficient as possible.

Input Parameters
post_urls: a list of tiktok post urls to scrape
Example input
{
  "post_info": [
    "https://www.tiktok.com/@olympics/video/7200420986661965061",
  ],
  "post_comments": [
    "https://www.tiktok.com/@olympics/video/7200420986661965061",
  ]
}

